about.LicenseAgreement: Adigoo isticmaalaya softiweerahan, waxaad ku raacsan tahay shuruudaha heshiiska shatiga softiweerka Neuralium. Waxaad ka daawan kartaa nooca ugu dambeeyay ee heshiiska liisanka softiweerka:

verifyAccount.Title: Xaqiijinta Koontada
verifyAccount.IntroductionText: Si looga hortago waxyeelada, hanaanka abuuritaanka koontada waa inuu maraa nooc xaqiijin ah. Waxay kuxirantahay meesha aad joogto, xulashooyin kaladuwan ayaa la heli karaa.
verifyAccount.ResultsSuccess: Xaqiijinta waxay ahayd guul! koontadaada Id hada waxaa lagu hubiyaa taleefanka.
verifyAccount.ResultsFailure: Xaqiijinta ayaa ahayd fashil. Waxaad isku dayi kartaa markale 24 saac gudahood.
verifyAccount.DefaultHelpText: Halkan waa inaad ku doorataa hab xaqiijin oo ka mid ah xulashooyinka la heli karo. Qaab kastaa wuxuu leeyahay faa'iidooyin iyo dhib la'aan. Fadlan soo xulo midka kugu habboon.
verifyAccount.TESTNETHelpText: Gudaha TESTNET, xaqiijinta waa lagala wareegi karaa si loogu sameeyo koonto isla markiiba.
verifyAccount.AppointmentsHelpText: Waxaad bilaabi doontaa nidaamka xaqiijinta magacaabista Neuralium. Hawshani waxay socon kartaa maalmo badan waana inaad joogi doontaa ballantaada marka taariikhda la xaqiijiyo. Faa'iidooyinka: magac la'aan
verifyAccount.POWHelpText: Waa inaad ku dhaqaaqdaa waqti caddayn qaali ah oo CPU ah oo shaqada ah. Markii la dhammeeyo, akaawnkaagu wuxuu awood u yeelan doonaa aniga 1-aad iyo 2-aad darajooyin Server ah.

appointments.Title: Xaqiijinta Ballanka
appointments.IntroductionText: Qulqulka shaqo ee ballanta waxaa loo habeeyay si loo xaqiijiyo isticmaaleyaasha la damacsan yahay iyadoo laga ilaaliyo inta badan daadadku inay nidaamka ka baxaan.
appointments.RequestAppointmentText: Si aad u bilowdo hawsha, fadlan codso ballan ballantu. Codsi ballan ayaa la sameyn doonaa waana in la xaqiijiyo mustaqbalka.
appointments.RequestCompleted: Codsiga ballanta si guul leh ayaa loo diray
appointments.VerificationRequestSent: Codsiga balanta balanta si guul ah ayaa loo diray
appointments.VerificationRequestCompleted: Codsiga xaqiijinta ballanta waa la xaqiijiyay.
appointments.VerificationRequestRejected: Codsiga balanta balanta waa la diiday.
appointments.AppointmentRequestedText: Ballantaadii dib ayaa loo soo celiyay. Waa inaan hadda sugno xaqiijinta.
appointments.AppointmentConfirmedText: Codsigaaga ballanta ayaa la xaqiijiyay oo taariikhda iyo waqtiga ballanka ayaa loo qabtay. Hubso inaad timaado wakhtiga!
appointments.AppointmentVerificationRequestedText: Codsiga balanta balanta waa la diray. Waxaan hadda sugeynaa xaqiijinta.
appointments.AppointmentVerificationCompletedText: Codsiga xaqiijinta ballanta waa la xaqiijiyay. Waad usii gudbi kartaa oo aad u daabacdaa akoonkaaga blockchain.
appointments.AppointmentVerificationRejectedText: Codsiga balanta balanta waa la diiday.

mining.Miningportalert: Fiiro gaar ah: Tan si aan u leeyahay, dekadaada TCP waa inay ku xirnaadaa noodh kale ee p2p ah. Wadaagistu waa akhlaaqda saxda ah ee p2p. Hadaad jeceshahay inaad leedahay anigoo leh qeybta labaad ee qodista macdanta iyo dekeda koowaad, dekada WAA INUU isku xirmi karaa hadii kale buundada waligeed kuma guuleysan doonto waxwalba. Fadlan hubso inaad furatid gidaarkaaga oo aad u suurtageliso gudbinta dekeda.

testMode.ParagrahOne: Adigu hadda waxaad ku sugan tahay habka 'TESTNET'. Nooca 'testnet' waxaa loogu tala galay in lagu tijaabiyo astaamo cusub oo laga yaabo ama u shaqeyn karin sidii loogu talagalay. Waxaad u soo sheegi kartaa wixii cayayaanka ah, dhibaatooyinka ama talo soo jeedinta ah ee aad ka qabi karto xallintayada heeganka leh.
testMode.ParagrahTwo: Qaabka 'TESTNET', nooc kasta oo tukumaannada neeralium laga helo waxaa loogu talagalay ujeedo tijaabo ah oo keliya loomana adeegsan karo soosaarka 'MainNet'. Tilmaamaha calaamadaha lagu helo habka TESTNET ayaa sidoo kale laga yaabaa inay lummaan ama dib loo dejiyo wakhti kasta iyadoon ogeysiis hore laga helin.
testMode.Warning: Nambarka iyo boorsada jeebka ayaa hadda ku jira ModNet Mode shabakad gaar ah.
testMode.Period: Dhismaha TESTNET wuxuu shaqeynayaa ilaa Ogost 18th 2020.
